    "en": {
      "title": "An early morning robbery in Pananturai",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Panantura North Police, gas cylinders worth more than ten lakh rupees and cash were stolen from the sale of Litro gas in Panantura North this morning.",
        "According to the complaint lodged by the owner of the shop, 30 gas cylinders and Rs 30,000 cash were also stolen from the shop.",
        "According to the police, investigation revealed that some people in the van used fake keys to open the front door and committed the theft.",
        "The theft was captured on a CCTV camera installed in the building in front of the shop."
      ],
